{{unsourced|date=January 2009}}
'''Ramon B. Neri''' was the Mayor of [[Cagayan de Oro|Cagayan de Misamis]] from 1912&ndash;1916 and represented [[Misamis]] during the [[4th Philippine Legislature]]. Together with his brother the late [[Misamis Oriental]] Governor Vicente Neri, they Founded the first weekly newspaper in [[Cagayan de Oro]] it was called ''Ang Katarungan''.

